    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A strong paper board containing no jute fiber but made typically from sulfate and wastepaper pulp, used especially for shipping containers.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
